<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.<br/><strong>Melee</strong> +1 human-bane scimitar +22/+17/+12 (1d6+10/18-20), mwk handaxe +20/+15 (1d6+6/&times;3)<br/><strong>Ranged</strong> dagger +21/+16/+11 (1d4+5/19-20)<br/><strong>Special Attacks</strong> weapon training (heavy blades +3, axes +2, light blades +1)</p>
